tIanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12818] fixed pipe redirection into 
``complete``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12817] fixed raw strings as external arguments
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12815] fixed syntax highlighting for 
``not``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12812] fixed/simplified cwd in benchmarks
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12799] refactored message printing in 
``rm``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12793] fixed list spread syntax highlighting
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12791] refactored 
``parse``
 command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12787] added 
``sys users``
 command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12783] passed 
``Stack``
 ref to 
``Completer::fetch``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12782] refactored the CLI code
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12770] refactored 
``describe``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12756] refactored flattening to reduce intermediate allocations
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12747] added 
``sys``
 subcommands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12524] touched up 
``ListStream``
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12669] refactored dataframes to be much more lazy about evaluation
.
YizhePKU 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12779] implemented PWD recovery
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12749] migrated to a new PWD API (part 2)
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12810] cleaned up osc calls for shell_integration
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12806] made the warning message clearer when running a plugin exe directly
.
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12784] shrunk 
``Value``
 by boxing 
``Range``
/
``Closure``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12771] added SOPs for dealing with adding deps/crates
.
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12776] allowed raw strings to be used inside subexpression, list, and closure
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12625] allowed 
``ls``
 to work inside dir with 
[
]
 brackets
.
cablehead 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12754] added an echo command to nu_plugin_example
.
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12717] improved NUON documentation
.
FilipAndersson245 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12469] migrated to the Tango benchmarking framework
.
